text: haey champoh puok yeahou ti yeung ban hamkhat( kar briphok) real satv del mean krachk cheabknea . haey champoh ko ryy ppe yeung ban hamkhat towleu puokke nouv kar briphok khlanh robsa vea leuklengte khlanh del cheab now nung chhaoengokhnang robsa vea ryy pohvien ryy khlanh del cheabnung chhaoeng teanglay bonnaoh . teangnoh ku yeung ban tabasnang champoh puokke daoy karbampean robsa puokke . haey pit brakd nasa yeung kuchea anak del brakean sachchathmr
